{212}{}{[离开] -- [Leave.]}
#{213}{}{It was an easy job, so there's not much pay. But if we pull this next job off, we're golden.}
{213}{}{这是一份容易的工作，所以薪水不多。但如果我们能完成下一个任务，我们就是黄金。 -- It was an easy job, so there's not much pay. But if we pull this next job off, we're golden.}
#{214}{}{Thanks for the cash, but what are you up to?}
{214}{}{谢谢你的现金，你在忙什么？ -- Thanks for the cash, but what are you up to?}
#{215}{}{Finally! So, what do I have to do to get rich?}
{215}{}{终于！那么，我要怎么做才能发财呢？ -- Finally! So, what do I have to do to get rich?}
#{216}{}{It's time to go for Thompson's throat. We've got to take the town hall, and you're gonna help us.}
{216}{}{是时候抓住汤普森的喉咙了。我们得去市政厅，你来帮我们。 -- It's time to go for Thompson's throat. We've got to take the town hall, and you're gonna help us.}
#{217}{}{Wait, you want me to attack Thompson's headquarters? I'm not much of a fighter, you know... }
{217}{}{等等，你想让我袭击汤普森的总部？我不是什么斗士，你知道。。。 -- Wait, you want me to attack Thompson's headquarters? I'm not much of a fighter, you know... }
#{218}{}{Wait, you want me to attack Thompson's headquarters? This is going to be awesome!}
{218}{}{等等，你想让我袭击汤普森的总部？这会很棒的！ -- Wait, you want me to attack Thompson's headquarters? This is going to be awesome!}
#{219}{}{Your photos show he's got video feeds in his bunker, and I know he's got reinforcements on radio. You're gonna take out the power in his bunker so we can catch him by surprise. Once you've done that, give the signal to my men. They'll be waiting near the town hall.}
{219}{}{你的照片显示他在地堡里有录像，我知道他在广播里有增援。你要切断他地堡里的电源，这样我们就能出其不意地抓住他。一旦你这么做了，给我的人信号。他们将在市政厅附近等候。 -- Your photos show he's got video feeds in his bunker, and I know he's got reinforcements on radio. You're gonna take out the power in his bunker so we can catch him by surprise. Once you've done that, give the signal to my men. They'll be waiting near the town hall.}
#{220}{}{Hmm... I wonder what Big Louie would say if he knew what you were doing?}
{220}{}{隐马尔可夫模型。。。我想知道如果大路易知道你在做什么，他会怎么说？ -- Hmm... I wonder what Big Louie would say if he knew what you were doing?}
#{221}{}{[His eyes narrow] Watch yourself. He already knows... Not that I care. I don't live to do his bitch work.}
{221}{}{[他眯着眼睛]小心点。他已经知道了。。。我不在乎。我活不下去做他那该死的工作。 -- [His eyes narrow] Watch yourself. He already knows... Not that I care. I don't live to do his bitch work.}
#{222}{}{Isn't he your boss?}
{222}{}{他不是你老板吗？ -- Isn't he your boss?}
#{223}{}{He's useful right now, so I keep him happy with a Christmas present here and there. But I'm more than able to do business without him.}
{223}{}{他现在很有用，所以我到处送他圣诞礼物让他开心。但是没有他我也能做生意。 -- He's useful right now, so I keep him happy with a Christmas present here and there. But I'm more than able to do business without him.}
#{224}{}{Christmas presents? Seriously?}
{224}{}{圣诞礼物？说真的？ -- Christmas presents? Seriously?}
#{225}{}{What are your plans for this war?}
{225}{}{你对这场战争有什么计划？ -- What are your plans for this war?}
#{226}{}{Thompson and you are from the same gang, right?}
{226}{}{汤普森和你是一伙的，对吧？ -- Thompson and you are from the same gang, right?}
#{227}{}{Why can't you work together with Thompson? Together, you could control the whole city.}
{227}{}{你为什么不能和汤普森一起工作？你们可以一起控制整个城市。 -- Why can't you work together with Thompson? Together, you could control the whole city.}
#{228}{}{Forget it, I don't want to dig into your life.}
{228}{}{算了吧，我不想深究你的生活。 -- Forget it, I don't want to dig into your life.}
#{229}{}{Yeah, seriously! You delivered the last one, didn't you? Big Louie needs chems, guns and ammo for his gang. He's practically begging. I need them too, but I can spare enough to maintain our relationship.}
{229}{}{是啊，说真的！你送了最后一个，是吗？大路易需要化学药品，枪支和弹药。他简直是在乞讨。我也需要他们，但我可以拿出足够的钱来维持我们的关系。 -- Yeah, seriously! You delivered the last one, didn't you? Big Louie needs chems, guns and ammo for his gang. He's practically begging. I need them too, but I can spare enough to maintain our relationship.}
#{230}{}{No one really knew what was coming when Big Louie took Reno. I didn't think it would be this goddamn *complicated*. You can't control Reno because *no one* controls Reno - the whole city's a bunch of small parts, every one with their own people and rules. We didn't have enough men to manage it all, especially since people were demanding changes from day one. It was chaos. Fuck, it still is!}
{230}{}{没人知道大路易带走雷诺的时候会发生什么。我没想到会这么复杂。你不能控制雷诺，因为没有人控制雷诺――整个城市都是一堆小地方，每个地方都有自己的人和规则。我们没有足够的人手来管理这一切，尤其是因为人们从第一天起就要求改变。一片混乱。妈的，还是这样！ -- No one really knew what was coming when Big Louie took Reno. I didn't think it would be this goddamn *complicated*. You can't control Reno because *no one* controls Reno - the whole city's a bunch of small parts, every one with their own people and rules. We didn't have enough men to manage it all, especially since people were demanding changes from day one. It was chaos. Fuck, it still is!}
#{231}{}{[Leave.]}
{231}{}{[离开] -- [Leave.]}
#{232}{}{The only choice is to set up a central authority and get everyone to fall in line. But the business leaders wouldn't want that, and they're the ones we need on our side. So, I'll have to make friends, make deals... Make it worth their while. They'll come around eventually. As soon as I get one in, they'll see the benefits and the others will follow.}
{232}{}{唯一的选择是建立一个中央权力机构，让每个人都服从。但商界领袖不希望这样，他们正是我们需要的人。所以，我要交朋友，做交易。。。让他们觉得值得。他们终究会回来的。我一进去，他们就会看到好处，其他人也会跟着进来。 -- The only choice is to set up a central authority and get everyone to fall in line. But the business leaders wouldn't want that, and they're the ones we need on our side. So, I'll have to make friends, make deals... Make it worth their while. They'll come around eventually. As soon as I get one in, they'll see the benefits and the others will follow.}
#{233}{}{The boss left each of us in charge of different parts of the city. But Thompson's a dreamer - he wants absolute power over everything in Reno. That includes me, and I don't like that idea. But even if he wanted to share power... We just couldn't. We're too goddamn different.}
{233}{}{老板让我们每个人负责城市的不同部分。但汤普森是一个梦想家-他想要在雷诺的一切绝对权力。包括我在内，我不喜欢这个主意。但即使他想分享权力。。。我们就是做不到。我们太不一样了。 -- The boss left each of us in charge of different parts of the city. But Thompson's a dreamer - he wants absolute power over everything in Reno. That includes me, and I don't like that idea. But even if he wanted to share power... We just couldn't. We're too goddamn different.}
#{234}{}{I live in the real world, he doesn't. He basically wants to be Reno's dictator. You wouldn't think that's a good way to make friends, but he's got a lot of support. It took me a while to figure out why - the common people here have *never* been free. Everyone's a slave, even if they don't call them that - to their employers, or their pimps, or their landlords, or their drug dealers. They don't know any other way to live, and Thompson uses that. But you know, the common people don't really matter. It's the business leaders you need on your side, and they don't want a dictator, which means it's *never* going to happen. We can't just wipe out our opponents in one night and put our own people in place - not in a city this size, with this many leaders. That gang war shit doesn't cut it on this scale. I've spent the last five years learning that.}
{234}{}{我生活在现实世界里，他没有。他基本上想成为雷诺的独裁者。你不会认为那是交朋友的好方法，但他得到了很多支持。我花了一段时间才弄明白为什么这里的老百姓从来没有自由过。每个人都是奴隶，即使他们不这么称呼他们――对他们的雇主，皮条客，房东，毒贩。他们不知道其他的生活方式，汤普森就是这样。但是你知道，普通人并不重要。你需要的是商界领袖，他们不想要独裁者，这意味着这是永远不会发生的。我们不能在一个晚上就消灭我们的对手，把我们自己的人安置到位――不能在这么大的城市，有这么多领导人。帮派战争这玩意可没这么厉害。我花了五年的时间学习这个。 -- I live in the real world, he doesn't. He basically wants to be Reno's dictator. You wouldn't think that's a good way to make friends, but he's got a lot of support. It took me a while to figure out why - the common people here have *never* been free. Everyone's a slave, even if they don't call them that - to their employers, or their pimps, or their landlords, or their drug dealers. They don't know any other way to live, and Thompson uses that. But you know, the common people don't really matter. It's the business leaders you need on your side, and they don't want a dictator, which means it's *never* going to happen. We can't just wipe out our opponents in one night and put our own people in place - not in a city this size, with this many leaders. That gang war shit doesn't cut it on this scale. I've spent the last five years learning that.}
#{240}{}{Once you're done your part, you can go. I don't need you to fight. I won't say no if you want to help, though. In the meantime, I'll get my people ready.}
{240}{}{一旦你完成了你的任务，你就可以走了。我不需要你打架。不过，如果你想帮忙，我不会拒绝的。同时，我会让我的人做好准备。 -- Once you're done your part, you can go. I don't need you to fight. I won't say no if you want to help, though. In the meantime, I'll get my people ready.}
#{241}{}{We've taken the town hall. Thompson is dead.}
{241}{}{我们占领了市政厅。汤普森死了。 -- We've taken the town hall. Thompson is dead.}
#{242}{}{Finally! [he sighs in relief] Reno's going to remember this day. It's the first day of the future! Makes me want to crack open a bottle of whiskey... But you deserve a lot more than that.}
{242}{}{终于！雷诺会记住这一天的。这是未来的第一天！让我想打开一瓶威士忌。。。但你应该得到更多。 -- Finally! [he sighs in relief] Reno's going to remember this day. It's the first day of the future! Makes me want to crack open a bottle of whiskey... But you deserve a lot more than that.}
#{243}{}{[Next.]}
{243}{}{[下一步。] -- [Next.]}
#{244}{}{[He counts out your payment] You know, I don't think anyone else in this place could have done what you did for me. I won't forget that. I'm telling everyone I work with to give you a discount, and if you ever need to use the lab, it's yours. If anyone in this city gives you shit, give them my name. It's about to get a lot more respected.}
{244}{}{[他数了数你的报酬]你知道，我不认为这个地方的其他人能像你为我做的那样。我不会忘记的。我告诉所有和我一起工作的人给你一个折扣，如果你需要使用实验室，那就是你的了。如果这个城市有人给你大便，告诉他们我的名字。它将得到更多的尊重。 -- [He counts out your payment] You know, I don't think anyone else in this place could have done what you did for me. I won't forget that. I'm telling everyone I work with to give you a discount, and if you ever need to use the lab, it's yours. If anyone in this city gives you shit, give them my name. It's about to get a lot more respected.}
