#{248}{}{Thanks, boss.}
{248}{}{谢谢，老板。 -- Thanks, boss.}
#{249}{}{[He nods] Good to see you.}
{249}{}{很高兴见到你。 -- [He nods] Good to see you.}
#{250}{}{Now, we got to get to work. I gotta get the business leaders under me while they're still off-balance over Thompson. It's not your kind of work, so I hope you can find something to keep you busy. I won't have any jobs for you for a long time.}
{250}{}{现在，我们得开始工作了。我得让商界领袖们在我的领导下，趁他们对汤普森还不平衡的时候。这不是你喜欢的工作，所以我希望你能找到一些让你忙的事情。我很长时间都没有工作给你了。 -- Now, we got to get to work. I gotta get the business leaders under me while they're still off-balance over Thompson. It's not your kind of work, so I hope you can find something to keep you busy. I won't have any jobs for you for a long time.}
#{251}{}{No problem, boss.}
{251}{}{没问题，老板。 -- No problem, boss.}
