{306}{}{嘿，各位，看看这个混蛋！哦，路易一定是疯了！[每个人都看着你窃笑] -- [Chuckles] Hey everyone, check out this bad motherfucker! Oh, Louie must be *really* mad! [everyone looks at you and snickers]}
